description:
Danny chats with Dr. Wendy from The Real Housewives of Potomac about the season, what's to come, her relationship with Karen, voting, and more! Then, Danny recaps the craziness on this week's Bachelorette, which featured a roast, a new bachelorette, and men in capris.


Wendy Interview: 2:00ish minutes

Bachelorette Recap: 32:00ish


PS Subscribe to Danny's spinoff podcast, A Very Merry Iconic Podcast, which launches season 2 on October 28!
